== Icelandic ==

=== Interjection ===

'''hæ'''

# [[hi]]

==== Usage note ====

The use of ''[[hæ]]'' and ''[[bæ]]'' (corresponding to English "hi" and "bye", respectively) is frowned upon, especially among older people. ''[[sæll]]/[[sæl]]'' and ''[[bless]]'' should be used instead.

